---

If you use this software in academic work, please cite:

  Jocelyn Li and Margaret Martonosi,
  "An Analysis of Speculative Window Decoders for Quantum Error Correction,"
  arXiv:2606.24048, 2026.

The underlying speculative window decoding algorithm builds on SWIPER (ISCA 2025).
This repository is a lightweight round-stepped analysis playground for the
Li & Martonosi paper and is not the full SWIPER-SIM release.